{{#> layout
  title='About'
  url='/about.html'
}}
  <div class="container-md mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-5 text-center">About</h1>

    <p>
      Vocably is an <a href="https://github.com/vocably/language-learning-tool" target="_blank" class="link-secondary">open-source<i class="bi bi-github ms-1"></i></a> dictionary and a language-learning tool created by a <a href="https://sneas.io" target="_blank" class="link-secondary">Ukrainian programmer</a> who lives in the Netherlands.
    </p>

    <style>
      .speech-bubble {
        font-size: 90%;
        background: var(--bs-gray-100);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        position: relative;
      }

      .speech-bubble::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: -10px;
        top: 3rem;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        border-top: 10px solid transparent;
        border-bottom: 10px solid transparent;
        border-right: 10px solid var(--bs-gray-100);

        @media (width < 576px) {
          top: 0;
          left: 3rem;
          width: 0;
          height: 0;
          border: 10px solid transparent;
          border-bottom-color: var(--bs-gray-100);
          border-top: 0;
          margin-top: -10px;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <dl class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row align-items-start" style="background: var(--bs-gray-200); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1.5rem; gap: 2rem">
      <dt><img src="assets/about.webp" class="rounded-circle" alt="Photo of Dima Snisarenko" width="120"/></dt>
      <style>
        .speech-bubble p {
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          &:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
          }
        }
      </style>
      <dd class="speech-bubble">
        <p>Vocably has helped me become a confident reader.</p>

        <p>
          Now, I’m working on my speaking skills, which are currently <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/learndutch/comments/1mhenyu/this_is_how_i_play_the_dutchman_how_did_i_perform/" target="_blank" class="link-secondary">terrible</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
          I develop Vocably almost exclusively for my own benefit, but it seems <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/15CfNa_Lp1HO5oZDPk4dofJP9cIJexlrnOXvvZ5dcaNo/edit?gid=0#gid=0" target="_blank" class="link-secondary">some other people</a> also find the project useful.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you believe that the best way to learn a language is by using it in daily life, then you might also appreciate Vocably.
        </p>

        <p>The app provides a cross-platform dictionary and a learning system.</p>

        <p>If you also have a reason to use a dictionary, then you probably also have a reason to use Vocably.</p>

        <p>Feel free to <a href="/de-en/apple-in-german.html" class="link-secondary">the online dictionary</a>.</p>
      </dd>
    </dl>
  </div>
{{/layout}}

